         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 29th June 1882 ¶ Mrs Robert Ramsay ¶ Madam ¶  ¶ At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held on the 26th inst. it was resolved unanimously, to convey to you the expression of condol...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.06.29a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Isabella Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A345 Royal Park<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Trustees<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter &amp; minute book, p.68, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 29th June 1882</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Mrs Robert Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Madam</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At a meeting of the Trustees of the Royal Park, held on the 26th inst. it was resolved unanimously, to convey to you the expression of condolence, felt by the Trustees at the loss sustained by you through the early and so unexpected death of their late respected colleague, the Hon. Robert Ramsay.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ramsay died on 23 May 1882.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>In transmitting to you this resolution, allow me to add, that the vivid interest evinced by the lamented gentleman also in all matters concerning the Royal Park and the ready and genial manner, in which he devoted his great talents and his valuable time to all public affairs in this colony, will always be kept in grateful remembrance by my colleagues of the Park-trust and myself.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor, Madam, to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your very obedient</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(signed) Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
